channel.title: Runescape botting
channel.description:
Hey, i am a botter on 'Runescape' and i know it's wrong and all... but who follows the rules today... so i was just wondering if any of you botters out their know were i can find a FREE runescape soul wars bot?? I was recently permanantly banned from runescape and i am trying to start a new account but killing chickens takes forever -.-... and i know that google and youtube doesn't work, because i've tried it tons of times... and 99.9% of those bots are keyloggers or some shit... Well Please dont flame this topic, just looking for a good 'free' soul wars bot... If you got one give me the link, would be appreciated... Thanks!!
:D
